{"tid":1603230,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台同事近月採訪遇警方武力對待　港台嚴厲譴責","createTime":"2019-09-29T15:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T15:43:11.000Z","uid":32577,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"761fac342d6de33233431a78937bb3d79cbcc691","tid":1603230,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:40:18.000Z","msg":"香港電台發言人表示，本台攝影助理今晚在正常採訪拍攝期間被阻撓，手部亦被警棍擊傷。<br />\n<br />\n就本台同事近月數次在採訪期間，都遇到警方武力對待，香港電台嚴厲譴責此等針對新聞記者之暴力行為，保留追究權利，並期望各方克制。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483269-20190929.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483269-20190929.htm&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=9bcf008a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483269-20190929.htm&h=770ff65c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483269-20190929.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cf685e2cdf090cc5400ccf76fa339705079670d6","tid":1603230,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:41:10.000Z","msg":"你地係咪當全地球人都係condom?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/efonbS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/efonbS</a><br />\n<br />\n929全球反共 成績表(持續更新)<br />\n集合全球反共各國既集會tweet 幫手retweet"},{"pid":"204d46098193ffdf5b1263ef9228b2cf5cd6a1d2","tid":1603230,"uid":128972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:42:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屎蟲</span></span><br />\n食屎大 個腦裝屎<br />\n叫狗其實侮辱咗啲狗狗"},{"pid":"794528ca9993c56844999af874f51001be6f06f3","tid":1603230,"uid":62192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"港台出完，跟住到記恊譴責"}]}